name: HENthousand dreams on the road to success
description: one of my most popular beats ive done. original features roc marciano, sketch mcguiney and reef the lost cauze, "chain smoking." The art is made using GAN on some vaporwave images & japanese cover art form the 70s/80s. Then hand selected stills create a looping image at the same pace of the beat. 78 stills, 78 Beats per minute
